messages.message:
@david.lee asking for pie charts / bar charts won't work unless the document text specifically mentions that there is a bar/pie chart, which from your screenshots, I don't see any mention of. I would ask for it to "describe recruitment trends" or "honors awarded". The TLDR is that you can't ask prompts that search in the visual space, since retrieval right now is only in the text space.

Let me create an EPD ticket to track these examples of visual provenance being incorrect
